doctype html
html(lang='en')
    head
        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible', content='IE=edge')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1')
        meta(name='description', content='')
        meta(name='author', content='')
        title TEC - #{name}
        // Bootstrap Core CSS
        link(href='css/bootstrap.min.css', rel='stylesheet')
        // Custom CSS
        link(href='css/shop-viewitempage.css', rel='stylesheet')
        // TEC CSS
        link(href='css/style.css', rel='stylesheet')
        // HTML5 Shim and Respond.js IE8 support of HTML5 elements and media queries
        // WARNING: Respond.js doesn't work if you view the page via file://
        //if lt IE 9
          script(src='https://oss.maxcdn.com/libs/html5shiv/3.7.0/html5shiv.js')
          script(src='https://oss.maxcdn.com/libs/respond.js/1.4.2/respond.min.js')
    body
        // Navigation
        nav.navbar.navbar-inverse.navbar-fixed-top(role='navigation')
            .container
                // Brand and toggle get grouped for better mobile display
                .navbar-header
                    button.navbar-toggle(type='button', data-toggle='collapse', data-target='#bs-example-navbar-collapse-1')
                        span.sr-only Toggle navigation
                        span.icon-bar
                        span.icon-bar
                        span.icon-bar
                    a.navbar-brand(href='/') TEC
                // Collect the nav links, forms, and other content for toggling
                #bs-example-navbar-collapse-1.collapse.navbar-collapse
                    ul.nav.navbar-nav.left
                        li
                            a(href='/browse') Browse
                        li
                            a(href='/contact') Contact
                        li
                    ul.nav.navbar-nav.right
                        li
                            a(href='/login') Login
                        li
                            a(href='/register') Register
                    .nav.navbar-nav.middle
                        input(id='searchBox', type='text', placeholder='Search...', required='', style='backgroundColor=#fff;', href='/search')
                        input(id='submitButton', type='button', value='Search')
                // /.navbar-collapse
            // /.container
        // Page Content
        .container
            .row
                .col-md-3
                    p.lead Top End Code
                    .list-group
                        a.list-group-item(href='#') Textbooks
                        a.list-group-item(href='#') Magazines
                        a.list-group-item(href='#') DVDs
                        a.list-group-item(href='#') Textbooks
                        a.list-group-item(href='#') Magazines
                        a.list-group-item(href='#') DVDs
                        a.list-group-item(href='#') Textbooks
                        a.list-group-item(href='#') Magazines
                        a.list-group-item(href='#') DVDs
                        a.list-group-item(href='#') Textbooks
                        a.list-group-item(href='#') Magazines
                        a.list-group-item(href='#') DVDs
                .col-md-9
                    a.itemName(href='/view?itemid=' + id) #{name}
                    .middle-container
                        .middle-container.description
                            //p #{description}
                            p Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nunc quis nisl felis. Curabitur porttitor tincidunt consectetur. Sed cursus nulla eget lorem lacinia, in interdum tellus rutrum. Donec a est ipsum. Praesent lacus odio, bibendum non erat eu, malesuada viverra dui. Aliquam tempus nibh orci, non congue nibh laoreet ut. In in suscipit arcu, eget dapibus tortor. Ut consequat, mauris at efficitur suscipit, orci massa tincidunt lectus, in iaculis justo tortor id enim. Nullam sit amet leo aliquet turpis porttitor viverra a quis tortor. Mauris maximus felis ac nisl vehicula, vel condimentum nulla efficitur. Vivamus id sollicitudin nisi. Sed scelerisque, metus sed viverra viverra, leo libero sodales tortor, eu sodales arcu velit ac purus.
                        .middle-container.image-and-info
                            img(id='product-image',src='http://placehold.it/320x250', alt='')
                            .caption
                                h4.item-price $#{price}
                                if stock < 0
                                        p.stock-left 
                                else
                                        p.stock-left Stock Left: #{stock}
                    .bottom-container
                        .bottom-container.ratings
                            p
                                if rating > 0
                                    span.glyphicon.glyphicon-star
                                else
                                    span.glyphicon.glyphicon-star-empty
                                if rating > 1.5
                                    span.glyphicon.glyphicon-star
                                else
                                    span.glyphicon.glyphicon-star-empty
                                if rating > 2.5
                                    span.glyphicon.glyphicon-star
                                else
                                    span.glyphicon.glyphicon-star-empty
                                if rating > 3.5
                                    span.glyphicon.glyphicon-star
                                else
                                    span.glyphicon.glyphicon-star-empty
                                if rating > 4.5
                                    span.glyphicon.glyphicon-star
                                else
                                    span.glyphicon.glyphicon-star-empty
                                |    #{reviews} reviews
                        .row
                            .ratings-list
                                each comment, index in comments
                                    .ratings-list-item
                                        .ratings-list-item.rating
                                            p
                                            if commentRatings[index] > 0
                                                span.glyphicon.glyphicon-star
                                            else
                                                span.glyphicon.glyphicon-star-empty
                                            if commentRatings[index] > 1.5
                                                span.glyphicon.glyphicon-star
                                            else
                                                span.glyphicon.glyphicon-star-empty
                                            if commentRatings[index] > 2.5
                                                span.glyphicon.glyphicon-star
                                            else
                                                span.glyphicon.glyphicon-star-empty
                                            if commentRatings[index] > 3.5
                                                span.glyphicon.glyphicon-star
                                            else
                                                span.glyphicon.glyphicon-star-empty
                                            if commentRatings[index] > 4.5
                                                span.glyphicon.glyphicon-star
                                            else
                                                span.glyphicon.glyphicon-star-empty
                                        .ratings-list-item.commenter-id
                                            p Commenter ID: #{commenterIDs[index]}
                                        .ratings-list-item.comment
                                            p #{comment}




        .container
            hr
            // Footer
            footer
                .row
                    .col-lg-12
                        p Copyright Â© TEC 2016
